📊 **Dashboard Image Placeholder**

Replace this file with your actual screenshot of the results dashboard (e.g., swarm performance charts, RYE scores bar graph, robot status heatmap) to make the README visually stunning.

**How to replace:**
1. Download your PNG.
2. On this repo page, click **Add file** > **Upload files**
3. Select your `optimus_tgrm_swarm_v2_results.png`
4. Commit changes.

It will then render perfectly above the features section.